<p>For 4 years I was responsible for the SDLC and semi-annual development, version control, build/make, test (unit, system, integration, IV&V, UA), distribution, release, and maintenance/support of the C/C++ Unix desktop and Burroughs mainframe software and satellite communications interface.</p>

