<p>I was recruited from there to <a target="_blank" href="https://galencollege.edu/">Galen College of Nursing</a>, where I led and grew the engineering and support team from 6 to 17, while building out networks, IT, and interactive classrooms on 8 new campuses, and virtualizing servers and applications in our hybrid cloud, network, and telecomm (VOIP and SDWAN).</p>
